About ${project.name}

  A Java implementation of the Active Directory
  {{{https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/archive/technet-wiki/24457.how-domain-controllers-are-located-in-windows}domain controller locator process}}.
  It integrates your Java JNDI/LDAP code into your Active Directory environment with ease.

